@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1
@username = test6
@password = A2345!

### Вход в систему (получаем sessionid куку)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login/
Content-Type: application/json
{
    "username": "{{username}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

# Пользователи
###
get http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/users/16/
Content-Type: application/json
# Authorization: Token 4d53c2a6481f51483ba751d694734cc227269068

###
get http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/users/1/
Content-Type: application/json
# Authorization: Token 70cc3c7f718950ca3138c74d7ec04d2b0bfcce41

###
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/users/9/
Content-Type: application/json
